metadata.name: QRDapp #1
metadata.description:
#Interactive NFT of QR Code Generator. 

This decentralized application (dApp) encodes your crypto wallet address and your NFT art into QR code. A pixel art drawn by AI is also included. 

The digital fungus decomposes the QR code gradually. The owner must choose whether to transfer this NFT to another wallet or let the QR code decay. 

[QRDapp.net](https://qrdapp.net)
